src/__tests__/ReconcilePage.test.tsx: Pre-existing TypeScript error — mock API object missing `openReconciliation`\n- [MEDIUM] step 10 frontend/src/components/ai/QueryAnswerCard.tsx: Commit sources still cannot deep-link to a specific plan because `RagSource` does not include a plan identifier; the current step requirement mentions commit-to-plan links, but the available data model does not support a reliable route target.\n\nFiles changed so far:\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/cost.json\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/sessions/continuous/relay-a/2026-03-26T04-47-46-137Z_72092699-d416-4051-8917-7a32e149dfa5.jsonl\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/state.json\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/steps/11\nfrontend/src/__tests__/SemanticSearchInput.test.tsx\nfrontend/src/components/ai/SemanticSearchInput.tsx\n\nWhen done, explain what you reviewed, what you changed (if anything), and your assessment.\n\nEnd with:\nVerdict: approve  — if the step is complete and correct, no more changes needed\nVerdict: changes_made  — if you made fixes or improvements\nVerdict: replan_needed  — if the step is structurally impossible to complete as planned and needs controller-managed replanning"}],"timestamp":1774504697977}}
